707/https://www.humanbeatbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/butterscotch-profile-1-620x420.jpg Butterscotch]<ref name=\"Butterscotch\">{{cite web|url=https://www.humanbeatbox.com/beatboxers/butterscotch/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612194706/https://www.humanbeatbox.com/beatboxers/butterscotch/|url-status=dead|archive-date=2019-06-12|title=Butterscotch/humanbeatbox.com |date=2014 }}</ref> \n''([[Butterscotch (performer)|Antoinette Clinton]])''<ref name=\"boots\" />\n| (unknown)\n| <ref name=\"human\" /><ref name=\"reddit\" />\n|-\n| 2nd BBBWC\n| 2009\n| rowspan=\"4\" align=\"left\" |{{Flagicon|GER}} [[Berlin]], [[Germany]]\n| {{Flagicon|GBR}} [https://web.archive.org/web/20190613200354/http://toworkorplay.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Bellatrix_3.jpg Bellatrix]\n''(Isabel Ehresmann)''<ref name=\"boots\" /><ref name=\"Bellatrix\">{{cite web|url=http://toworkorplay.com/work/interviews/career-profiles/career-profile-bellatrix/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701074518/http://toworkorplay.com/work/interviews/career-profiles/career-profile-bellatrix/|url-status=dead|archive-date=2017-07-01|title=Bellatrix/toworkorplay.com |date=2015 }}</ref>\n| {{Flagicon|SWI} [https://web.archive.org/web/20190612190913/https://www.humanbeatbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/steff-la-cheffe-profile-1-620x420.jpg Steff la Cheffe]<ref name=\"Steff\">{{cite web|url=https://www.humanbeatbox.com/beatboxers/steff-la-cheffe/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612190912/https://www.humanbeatbox.com/beatboxers/steff-la-cheffe/|url-status=dead|archive-date=2019-06-12|title=Steff la Cheffe/humanbeatbox.com |date=2014 }}</ref>\n|\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qV5iCFpdBUY 2nd BBBWC Ladies Final 2009 (Youtube)]<ref name=\"human\" /><ref name=\"reddit\" />\n|-\n| 3rd BBBWC\n| 2012\n|'''{{Flagicon|BUL}}''' [https://web.archive.org/web/20190501085016/https://www.humanbeatbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/pe4enkata-profile-1.jpg Pe4enkata]<ref name=\"Pe4enka