 daily passengers used this service.<ref name=\"railjournal\">{{cite web|url= https://www.railjournal.com/africa/krc-to-order-new-dmus-for-nairobi-commuter-rail-network/|title=KRC to order new DMUs for Nairobi Commuter Rail network |website=International Railway Journal|date=11 January 2019|accessdate=29 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Services ==\n{{routemap\n| title       = Nairobi Commuter Rail Map\n| title color =\n| title bg    =\n| collapsible = yes\n| collapse    =\n| navbar      =\n| navbar pos  =\n| navbar mini =\n| legend      =\n| legend alt  =\n| float       = right\n| bg          =\n| style       =\n| top         =\n| footnote    =\n| text-width  =\n| map =\nCONTg~~ ~~ ~~''to [[Kijabe]]''\nHST~~[[Kikuyu, Kenya|Kikuyu]]\nHST~~[[Dagoretti]]\nHST~~[[Kibera]]\npHST~~[[Laini Saba]]\n{{BSsplit|''Kikuyu&ndash;''|''Nairobi line''}}~~ ~~! !bSHI2lr\nYRD!~GRZq\\GRZq!~INT~~ ~~{{rws|Nairobi}}~~ ~~{{rint|bus|1|link=Nairobi#Buses}}{{rint|air|link=Wilson Airport}}\nbSHI2+lr\n''Makadara Yard''~~ ~~! !YRDq\\ENDEeq!~HST\\~~[[Makadara Constituency|Makadara]]\nSTRc2\\ABZ3l!~num1r\\STR+r!~num2re~~{{BSsplit|1: ''Syokimau&ndash;Nairobi line''|2: ''Ruiru&ndash;Nairobi line''}}\n{{rws|Donholm}}! !STR+1\\HST+4!~num3l\\STR~~ ~~ ~~3: ''Embakasi&ndash;Nairobi line''\n{{rws|Tassia}}! !STR\\HST\\HST~~{{rws|Mutindwa}}\n{{rws|Pipeline}}! !STR\\HST\\HST~~{{rws|Kariobangi South}}\n{{rws|Imara Daima}}! !HST\\STR\\HST~~[[Dandora]]\n{{rint|air|link=Jomo Kenyatta International Airport}}~~ ~~[[Embakasi#Transport|Embakasi]]~~! !STR\\KINTe\\HST~~{{rws|Maili Saba}}\n{{rint|rail|link=Mombasa\u2013Nairobi Standard Gauge Railway}}~~ ~~[[Syokimau#Transport|Syokimau]]~~! !INT\\\\HST~~{{rws|Mwiki}}\n''to [[Mombasa]]''~~ ~~! !CONTf\\\\HST~~[[Githurai]]\n\\\\HST~~[[Kahawa#Transport|Kahawa]]\n\\\\HST~~[[Kenyatta University]]\n\\\\HST~~[[Ruiru]]\n\\\\CONTf~~ ~~ ~~''to [[Nanyuki]]''\n}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+Services\n|-\n! Name\n! Intermediate stops\n! Daily ridership\n! Services per day\n! Averag